---
/**
 * Company: EonHive Inc.
 * Title: Runtime Log Panel
 * Purpose: Render a bounded event log shell for the live URK example page.
 * Author: Stan Nesi
 * Created: 2026-05-01
 * Updated: 2026-05-14
 * Notes: Vibe coded with Codex.
 */
---

<section class="site-card flex flex-col gap-4 p-6">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
    <div>
      <div class="site-kicker">Runtime log</div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em]">Recent emitted events</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="m-0 max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-[var(--urk-muted)]">
      The panel shows recent kernel, loading, and controller events so the example proves URK’s
      runtime visibility instead of hiding behavior behind static marketing copy.
    </p>
  </div>

  <ol class="site-grid m-0 list-none p-0" data-role="runtime-event-list" aria-label="Recent runtime events">
    <li class="runtime-log-item">
      <div class="runtime-log-item__meta">
        <span>--:--:--</span>
        <span>kernel</span>
      </div>
      <strong>kernel:init</strong>
      <span>Waiting for runtime activity.</span>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>
